videos.description: Tennessee's Grant Williams finds Kyle Alexander in the post and he does the rest with a one-handed jam.
videos.headline: Alexander slams it home

videos.description: Tennessee's Admiral Schofield takes the feed from Jordan Bowden and powers through the defense for an and-1 layup.
videos.headline: Schofield flexes on the and-1 bucket

videos.description: Kevarrius Hayes finishes off a great defensive possession by Florida with a monster block on Grant Williams.
videos.headline: Hayes with monster block

videos.description: Tennessee gets the home crowd hyped with a lob from Jordan Bone to Jordan Bowden for the monster dunk.
videos.headline: Bowden gets crowd rocking with alley-oop

videos.description: Tennessee's Admiral Schofield gets it started with a monster putback dunk off a miss and follows that up with an even louder dunk.
videos.headline: Schofield throws down two monster jams
